WEBVTT

00:00:13.210 --> 00:00:15.240
Keep going, keep going, keep going!

00:00:16.080 --> 00:00:16.990
I'm going for it!

00:00:23.170 --> 00:00:25.600
On the outside, and just barely!

00:00:28.440 --> 00:00:32.570
Arima, Arima, Arima...

00:00:32.570 --> 00:00:35.930
Let's run at the Arima...

